title: Divisional-Round Preview
description:
Benjamin, Kaelen, and Steven discuss, dissect, and share their picks for all of the divisional-round NFL playoff matchups.
Chiefs-Bills (2:00)
Packers-49ers (17:46)
Rams-Buccaneers (30:08)
Bengals-Titans (39:23)
Hosts: Benjamin Solak, Kaelen Jones, Steven Ruiz
Production Assistant: Chris Sutton
Additional Production Supervision: Arjuna Ramgopal
